From stdpp Require Import prelude.
From Coq Require Import Eqdep Lia.
From VLSM Require Import Lib.Preamble Lib.ListExtras.
From VLSM Require Import Core.VLSM Core.VLSMProjections Core.Equivocators.Common.

VLSM Projecting Equivocator Traces

Section equivocator_vlsm_projections.
Given an equivocator_vlsm trace ending in a state s, we can obtain a trace in the original vlsm leading to the si, the ith internal state in s, by extracting a path leading to si.
This section is devoting to formalizing this projects studying its properties. In particular, we show that given a valid_trace for the equivocator_vlsm, we can always extract such a trace for any valid index, and, furthermore, that the trace extracted is valid for the original machine. 
Context
  {message : Type}
  (X : VLSM message)
  (equivocator_vlsm := equivocator_vlsm X)
  (MachineDescriptor := MachineDescriptor X)
  .
Given a transition_item item for the equivocator_vlsm and a MachineDescriptor referring to a position in the destination of item, it returns a transition item for the original machine (if the descriptor matches the copy affected by this transition) and a new machine descriptor referring to a position in the state prior to the transition. 
Definition equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project
  (item : vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
  (descriptor : MachineDescriptor)
  : option (option (vtransition_item X) * MachineDescriptor)
  :=
  match descriptor with
  | NewMachine _ => Some (None, descriptor)
  | Existing j =>
    match item with {| l := el; input := im; output := om; destination := s |} =>
      match equivocator_state_project s j with
      | None => None
      | Some sj =>
        match el with
        | Spawn sn =>
          if (decide (j = equivocator_state_last s)) then (* this is the first state *)
            Some (None, NewMachine sn)
          else Some (None, Existing j)
        | ForkWith i lx =>
            if (decide (j = equivocator_state_last s)) then (* this is the copy *)
              Some (Some {| l := lx; input := im; output := om; destination := sj|}, Existing i)
            else Some (None, Existing j)
        | ContinueWith i lx =>
          if decide (i = j) then
              Some ( Some {| l := lx; input := im; output := om; destination := sj|}, Existing i)
            else Some (None, Existing j)
        end
      end
    end
  end.
Since equivocators always have machine 0, We can always project a 'valid' equivocator 'transition item' to component 0.

X: VLSM message

Ht: vtransition equivocator_vlsm 
  (l item) (s, input item) =
(destination item, output item)
Hv: vvalid equivocator_vlsm (l item) (s, input item)
‚àÉ oitem : option (vtransition_item X),
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item
    (Existing 0) = Some (oitem, Existing 0)

n: nat
v: vlabel X
input: option message
destination: state
output: option message
s: state
Ht: match equivocator_state_project s n with
| Some si =>
    let (si', om') :=
      vtransition X v (si, input) in
    (equivocator_state_update s n si', om')
| None => (s, input)
end = (destination, output)
Hv: match equivocator_state_project s n with
| Some si => vvalid X v (si, input)
| None => False
end
‚àÉ oitem : option (vtransition_item X),
  match equivocator_state_project destination 0 with
  | Some sj =>
      if decide (n = 0)
      then
       Some
         (Some
            {|
              l := v;
              input := input;
              destination := sj;
              output := output
            |}, Existing n)
      else Some (None, Existing 0)
  | None => None
  end = Some (oitem, Existing 0)

| {|
    l := el;
    input := im;
    destination := s;
    output := om
  |} =>
    match equivocator_state_project s j with
    | Some sj =>
        match el with
        | Spawn sn =>
            if
             decide
               (j = equivocator_state_last s)
            then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
            else Some (None, Existing j)
        | ContinueWith i lx =>
            if decide (i = j)
            then
             Some
               (Some
                  {|
                    l := lx;
                    input := im;
                    destination := sj;
                    output := om
                  |}, Existing i)
            else Some (None, Existing j)
        | ForkWith i lx =>
            if
             decide
               (j = equivocator_state_last s)
            then
             Some
               (Some
                  {|
                    l := lx;
                    input := im;
                    destination := sj;
                    output := om
                  |}, Existing i)
            else Some (None, Existing j)
        end
    | None => None
    end

  Existing j = Existing i

      ‚àß output item = output itemX

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
l: label
input: option message
destination: state
output: option message
itemX: vtransition_item X
j: nat
odescriptor: MachineDescriptor
v: vstate X
Hitem: match l with
| Spawn sn =>
    if
     decide
       (j = equivocator_state_last destination)
    then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
    else Some (None, Existing j)
| ContinueWith i lx =>
    if decide (i = j)
    then
     Some
       (Some
          {|
            l := lx;
            input := input;
            destination := v;
            output := output
          |}, Existing i)
    else Some (None, Existing j)
| ForkWith i lx =>
    if
     decide
       (j = equivocator_state_last destination)
    then
     Some
       (Some
          {|
            l := lx;
            input := input;
            destination := v;
            output := output
          |}, Existing i)
    else Some (None, Existing j)
end = Some (Some itemX, odescriptor)
is_Some (Some v)
‚àß input = VLSM.input itemX
  ‚àß output = VLSM.output itemX

              else equivocator_state_s s 0%fin)
             (equivocator_state_project
                (equivocator_state_update s i si') i);
         output := output
       |}, Existing i)

    split; [eexists|];reflexivity.
Qed.
This property attempts to characterize the descriptor obtained after applying an equivocator projection (trace, transition_item) function in terms of the input descriptor and the resulting state.
It is assumed that the original_descriptor is a proper descriptor w.r.t. the final state of the trace/transition on which equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project or equivocator_vlsm_trace_project was applied. In particular this makes s_descriptor a proper descriptor for the state s (see the lemmas above and below).
What this property adds is the fact that it constrains more the output descriptor of a projection operation in terms of the input descriptor (if the input is Newmachine, the output must be Newmachine, if both are Existing, then the output index must be less than the input), while also guaranteeing that the output state of such a projection has a size less than the index of the input descriptor in case that output descriptor becomes NewMachine (signaling that the projection is complete).
This property is crucial for establishing an invariant on known equivocators (see full_node_limited_equivocation_constraint_known_equivocators). 
Definition previous_state_descriptor_prop
  (original_descriptor : MachineDescriptor)
  (s : vstate equivocator_vlsm)
  (s_descriptor : MachineDescriptor)
  : Prop :=
    match original_descriptor with
    | NewMachine sd => s_descriptor = original_descriptor
    | Existing id =>
      match s_descriptor with
      | NewMachine _ => equivocator_state_n s <= id
      | Existing id' => id' <= id
      end
    end.


message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
item: vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm
descriptor: MachineDescriptor
Hproper: proper_descriptor X descriptor
  (destination item)
‚àÉ (oitem : option (vtransition_item X)) (descriptor' : MachineDescriptor),
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item
    descriptor = Some (oitem, descriptor')
  ‚àß match oitem with
    | Some itemx =>
        (‚àÉ Hex : existing_equivocator_label X (l item),
           l itemx =
           existing_equivocator_label_extract X
             (l item) Hex)
        ‚àß input item = input itemx
          ‚àß output item = output itemx
            ‚àß equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                (destination item) descriptor =
              destination itemx
              ‚àß descriptor' =
                equivocator_label_descriptor (l item)
    | None => True
    end
    ‚àß (‚àÄ s : vstate equivocator_vlsm,
         vvalid equivocator_vlsm (l item)
           (s, input item)
         ‚Üí vtransition equivocator_vlsm (l item)
             (s, input item) =
           (destination item, output item)
           ‚Üí proper_descriptor X descriptor' s
             ‚àß previous_state_descriptor_prop
                 descriptor s descriptor'
               ‚àß match oitem with
                 | Some itemx =>
                     ‚àÄ sx : vstate X,
                       sx =
                       equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                         s descriptor'
                       ‚Üí vvalid X (l itemx)
                           (sx, input itemx)
                         ‚àß vtransition X (l itemx)
                             (sx, input itemx) =
                           (destination itemx,
                           output itemx)
                 | None =>
                     equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                       (destination item) descriptor =
                     equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                       s descriptor'
                 end)

Heqvi: descriptor = NewMachine v
Hproper: proper_descriptor X (NewMachine v)
  destination
‚àÉ (oitem : option (vtransition_item X)) (descriptor' : MachineDescriptor),
  Some (None, NewMachine v) =
  Some (oitem, descriptor')
  ‚àß match oitem with
    | Some itemx =>
        (‚àÉ Hex : existing_equivocator_label X l,
           VLSM.l itemx =
           existing_equivocator_label_extract X l Hex)
        ‚àß input = VLSM.input itemx
          ‚àß output = VLSM.output itemx
            ‚àß v = VLSM.destination itemx
              ‚àß descriptor' =
                equivocator_label_descriptor l
    | None => True
    end
    ‚àß (‚àÄ s : Common.bounded_state_copies X,
         equivocator_valid X l (s, input)

  Some
    {|
      l := li;
      input := input;
      destination := destn;
      output := output
    |}
with

               (ContinueWith n li),
       l itemx =
       existing_equivocator_label_extract X
         (ContinueWith n li) Hex)

      ‚àß output = VLSM.output itemx
        ‚àß default (equivocator_state_zero destination)
            (Some destn) = VLSM.destination itemx

            equivocator_label_descriptor
              (ContinueWith n li)
| None => True
end
‚àß (‚àÄ s : Common.bounded_state_copies X,
     equivocator_valid X (ContinueWith n li)
       (s, input)

         (s, input) = (destination, output)

         ‚àß match Existing n with
           | NewMachine _ => equivocator_state_n s ‚â§ n
           | Existing id' => id' ‚â§ n
           end

               Some

                   input := input;
                   destination := destn;
                   output := output
                 |}

                     s (Existing n)

  Some

    |}

            equivocator_label_descriptor
              (ForkWith ieqvi li)
| None => True
end
‚àß (‚àÄ s : Common.bounded_state_copies X,
     equivocator_valid X (ForkWith ieqvi li)
       (s, input)

                   output := output

                     vtransition X 
                      (l itemx) 
                      (sx, input itemx) =
                     (destination itemx,

                 equivocator_state_descriptor_project

                 equivocator_state_descriptor_project

The projection of an equivocator_vlsm trace is obtained by traversing the trace from right to left guided by the descriptors produced by equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project and gathering all non-empty transition_items it produces. 
Definition equivocator_vlsm_trace_project
  (tr : list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm))
  (descriptor : MachineDescriptor)
  : option (list (vtransition_item X) * MachineDescriptor)
  :=
  fold_right
    (fun item result =>
      match result with
      | None => None
      | Some (r, idescriptor) =>
        match equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item idescriptor with
        | None => None
        | Some (None, odescriptor) => Some (r, odescriptor)
        | Some (Some item', odescriptor) => Some (item' :: r, odescriptor)
        end
      end
    )
    (Some ([], descriptor))
    tr.
Projecting on a NewMachine descriptor yields an empty trace and the same descriptor. 
message: Type
X: VLSM message

tr: list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
s: vstate X
equivocator_vlsm_trace_project tr (NewMachine s) =
Some ([], NewMachine s)

  (NewMachine s) = Some ([], NewMachine s)
match
  equivocator_vlsm_trace_project tr (NewMachine s)
with
| Some (r, idescriptor) =>
    match
      equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project a
        idescriptor
    with
    | Some (Some item', odescriptor) =>

        Some (r, odescriptor)
    | None => None
    end
| None => None
end = Some ([], NewMachine s)

bsuffix: list (vtransition_item equivocator_vlsm)
dstart, dlast: MachineDescriptor
tr: list (vtransition_item X)
dmiddle: MachineDescriptor
Hsuffix: equivocator_vlsm_trace_project bsuffix dlast =
Some (tr, dmiddle)
Hprefix: equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project
  bprefix dmiddle = Some (None, dstart)
match
  equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project bprefix
    dmiddle
with
| Some (Some item', odescriptor) =>
    Some ([item'], odescriptor)
| Some (None, odescriptor) => Some ([], odescriptor)
| None => None
end = Some ([], dstart)

  l := l;
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom
|}: transition_item
i: nat
di': MachineDescriptor
item': vtransition_item X
Hitem: equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item
  (Existing i) = Some (Some item', di')
‚àÉ i0 : nat,
  Existing i = Existing i0
  ‚àß (‚àÉ sx : vstate X,
       equivocator_state_project s i0 = Some sx
       ‚àß (‚àÉ i' : nat,
            di' = Existing i'
            ‚àß (‚àÉ s'x : vstate X,
                 equivocator_state_project s' i' =
                 Some s'x
                 ‚àß (‚àÉ Hex : existing_equivocator_label
                              X l,
                      let lx :=
                        existing_equivocator_label_extract
                          X l Hex in
                      item' =
                      {|
                        l := lx;
                        input := iom;
                        destination := sx;
                        output := oom
                      |}
                      ‚àß vvalid X lx (s'x, iom)
                        ‚àß vtransition X lx (s'x, iom) =
                          (sx, oom)))))

  l := l;
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom
|}: transition_item
i: nat
di': MachineDescriptor
item': vtransition_item X
Hitem: match equivocator_state_project s i with
| Some sj =>
    match l with
    | Spawn sn =>
        if
         decide (i = equivocator_state_last s)
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | ContinueWith i0 lx =>
        if decide (i0 = i)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := iom;
                destination := sj;
                output := oom
              |}, Existing i0)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | ForkWith i0 lx =>
        if
         decide (i = equivocator_state_last s)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := iom;
                destination := sj;
                output := oom
              |}, Existing i0)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    end
| None => None
end = Some (Some item', di')
‚àÉ sx : vstate X,
  equivocator_state_project s i = Some sx
  ‚àß (‚àÉ i' : nat,
       di' = Existing i'
       ‚àß (‚àÉ s'x : vstate X,
            equivocator_state_project s' i' = Some s'x
            ‚àß (‚àÉ Hex : existing_equivocator_label X l,
                 let lx :=
                   existing_equivocator_label_extract
                     X l Hex in
                 item' =
                 {|
                   l := lx;
                   input := iom;
                   destination := sx;
                   output := oom
                 |}
                 ‚àß vvalid X lx (s'x, iom)
                   ‚àß vtransition X lx (s'x, iom) =
                     (sx, oom))))

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
l: vlabel equivocator_vlsm
s, s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom, oom: option message
Hv: vvalid equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom)
Ht: vtransition equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom) =
(s, oom)
item:= {|
  l := l;
  input := iom;
  destination := s;
  output := oom
|}: transition_item
di, di': MachineDescriptor
Hitem: equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item
  di = Some (None, di')
match di with
| NewMachine _ => di' = di
| Existing i =>
    match di' with
    | NewMachine sn' =>
        l = Spawn sn'
        ‚àß i = equivocator_state_last s
          ‚àß iom = None
            ‚àß oom = None
              ‚àß equivocator_state_project s i =
                Some sn' ‚àß vinitial_state_prop X sn'
    | Existing i' =>
        ‚àÉ si : vstate X,
          equivocator_state_project s i = Some si
          ‚àß equivocator_state_project s' i' = Some si
    end
end

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
l: vlabel equivocator_vlsm
s, s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom, oom: option message
Hv: vvalid equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom)
Ht: vtransition equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom) =
(s, oom)
i: nat
di': MachineDescriptor
Hitem: match equivocator_state_project s i with
| Some sj =>
    match l with
    | Spawn sn =>
        if
         decide (i = equivocator_state_last s)
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | ContinueWith i0 lx =>
        if decide (i0 = i)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := iom;
                destination := sj;
                output := oom
              |}, Existing i0)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | ForkWith i0 lx =>
        if
         decide (i = equivocator_state_last s)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := iom;
                destination := sj;
                output := oom
              |}, Existing i0)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    end
| None => None
end = Some (None, di')
match di' with
| NewMachine sn' =>
    l = Spawn sn'
    ‚àß i = equivocator_state_last s
      ‚àß iom = None
        ‚àß oom = None
          ‚àß equivocator_state_project s i = Some sn'
            ‚àß vinitial_state_prop X sn'
| Existing i' =>
    ‚àÉ si : vstate X,
      equivocator_state_project s i = Some si
      ‚àß equivocator_state_project s' i' = Some si
end

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
l: vlabel equivocator_vlsm
s, s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom, oom: option message
Hv: vvalid equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom)
Ht: vtransition equivocator_vlsm l (s', iom) =
(s, oom)
i': nat
si': vstate X
Hi': equivocator_state_project s' i' = Some si'
‚àÉ si : vstate X,
  equivocator_state_project s i' = Some si
  ‚àß (‚àÉ oitem : option (vtransition_item X),
       match equivocator_state_project s i' with
       | Some sj =>
           match l with
           | Spawn sn =>
               if
                decide (i' = equivocator_state_last s)
               then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
               else Some (None, Existing i')
           | ContinueWith i lx =>
               if decide (i = i')
               then
                Some
                  (Some
                     {|
                       l := lx;
                       input := iom;
                       destination := sj;
                       output := oom
                     |}, Existing i)
               else Some (None, Existing i')
           | ForkWith i lx =>
               if
                decide (i' = equivocator_state_last s)
               then
                Some
                  (Some
                     {|
                       l := lx;
                       input := iom;
                       destination := sj;
                       output := oom
                     |}, Existing i)
               else Some (None, Existing i')
           end
       | None => None
       end = Some (oitem, Existing i'))

‚àÉ (i : nat) (si : option (vstate X)),
  equivocator_state_project

      equivocator_state_project

    with

            equivocator_state_last

        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | None => None

equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom: option message
sn: state
item:= {|
  l := Spawn sn;
  input := iom;
  destination := equivocator_state_extend s' sn;
  output := None
|}: transition_item
Ht: vtransition equivocator_vlsm (Spawn sn) (s', iom) =
(equivocator_state_extend s' sn, None)
‚àÉ (i : nat) (si : option (vstate X)),
  equivocator_state_project
    (equivocator_state_extend s' sn) i = si
  ‚àß match
      equivocator_state_project
        (equivocator_state_extend s' sn) i
    with
    | Some _ =>
        if
         decide
           (i =
            equivocator_state_last
              (equivocator_state_extend s' sn))
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing i)
    | None => None
    end = Some (None, NewMachine sn)

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom: option message
sn: state
item:= {|
  l := Spawn sn;
  input := iom;
  destination := equivocator_state_extend s' sn;
  output := None
|}: transition_item
‚àÉ si : option (vstate X),
  equivocator_state_project
    (equivocator_state_extend s' sn)
    (equivocator_state_n s') = si
  ‚àß match
      equivocator_state_project
        (equivocator_state_extend s' sn)
        (equivocator_state_n s')
    with
    | Some _ =>
        if
         decide
           (equivocator_state_n s' =
            equivocator_state_n s')
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else
         Some
           (None, Existing (equivocator_state_n s'))
    | None => None
    end = Some (None, NewMachine sn)

  
message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom: option message
sn: state
item:= {|
  l := Spawn sn;
  input := iom;
  destination := equivocator_state_extend s' sn;
  output := None
|}: transition_item
‚àÉ si : option (vstate X),
  Some sn = si
  ‚àß (if
      decide
        (equivocator_state_n s' =
         equivocator_state_n s')
     then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
     else
      Some (None, Existing (equivocator_state_n s'))) =
    Some (None, NewMachine sn)

  
message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
s': vstate equivocator_vlsm
iom: option message
sn: state
item:= {|
  l := Spawn sn;
  input := iom;
  destination := equivocator_state_extend s' sn;
  output := None
|}: transition_item
(if
  decide
    (equivocator_state_n s' = equivocator_state_n s')
 then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
 else Some (None, Existing (equivocator_state_n s'))) =
Some (None, NewMachine sn)

  rewrite decide_True; reflexivity.
Qed.

           l := lx;
           input := iom;
           destination := si';
           output := oom
         |}, Existing _i)

  Some (Some itemx, Existing _i)

    (descriptor' : MachineDescriptor),
    equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project
      item (Existing i) =
    Some (oitem, descriptor')
    ‚àß match oitem with
      | Some itemx =>
          (‚àÉ Hex : existing_equivocator_label
                     X 
                     (VLSM.l item),
             VLSM.l itemx =
             existing_equivocator_label_extract
               X (VLSM.l item) Hex)
          ‚àß input item = input itemx
            ‚àß output item = output itemx
              ‚àß equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                  (destination item)
                  (Existing i) =
                destination itemx
                ‚àß descriptor' =
                  equivocator_label_descriptor
                    (VLSM.l item)
      | None => True
      end
      ‚àß (‚àÄ s : vstate equivocator_vlsm,
           vvalid equivocator_vlsm
             (VLSM.l item) 
             (s, input item)
           ‚Üí vtransition equivocator_vlsm
               (VLSM.l item) 
               (s, input item) =
             (destination item, output item)

                 s
               ‚àß previous_state_descriptor_prop
                   (Existing i) s descriptor'
                 ‚àß match oitem with

                      ‚àÄ sx : vstate X,
                      sx =
                      equivocator_state_descriptor_project
                      s descriptor'

| None => None

     {|

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
suffix: list transition_item
l: label
input: option message
destination: state
output: option message
j: nat
trX: list (vtransition_item X)
d, dmiddle: MachineDescriptor
itemx: vtransition_item X
Hx': match
  equivocator_state_project destination j
with
| Some sj =>
    match l with
    | Spawn sn =>
        if
         decide
           (j =
            equivocator_state_last destination)
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    | ContinueWith i lx =>
        if decide (i = j)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := input;
                destination := sj;
                output := output
              |}, Existing i)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    | ForkWith i lx =>
        if
         decide
           (j =
            equivocator_state_last destination)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := input;
                destination := sj;
                output := output
              |}, Existing i)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    end
| None => None
end = Some (Some itemx, dmiddle)

‚àÉ sj : vstate X,
  equivocator_state_project
    (VLSM.destination
       {|
         l := l;
         input := input;
         destination := destination;
         output := output
       |}) j = Some sj

Hx': match l with
| Spawn sn =>
    if
     decide
       (j = equivocator_state_last destination)
    then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
    else Some (None, Existing j)
| ContinueWith i lx =>
    if decide (i = j)
    then
     Some
       (Some
          {|
            l := lx;
            input := input;
            destination := v;
            output := output
          |}, Existing i)
    else Some (None, Existing j)
| ForkWith i lx =>
    if
     decide
       (j = equivocator_state_last destination)
    then
     Some
       (Some
          {|
            l := lx;
            input := input;
            destination := v;
            output := output
          |}, Existing i)
    else Some (None, Existing j)

message: Type
X: VLSM message
equivocator_vlsm:= Common.equivocator_vlsm X: VLSM message
MachineDescriptor:= Common.MachineDescriptor X: Type
suffix: list transition_item
l: EquivocatorLabel X
input: option message
destination: Common.bounded_state_copies X
output: option message
j: nat
trX: list (vtransition_item X)
d, dmiddle: MachineDescriptor
Hx': match
  equivocator_state_project destination j
with
| Some sj =>
    match l with
    | Spawn sn =>
        if
         decide
           (j =
            equivocator_state_last destination)
        then Some (None, NewMachine sn)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    | ContinueWith i lx =>
        if decide (i = j)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := input;
                destination := sj;
                output := output
              |}, Existing i)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    | ForkWith i lx =>
        if
         decide
           (j =
            equivocator_state_last destination)
        then
         Some
           (Some
              {|
                l := lx;
                input := input;
                destination := sj;
                output := output
              |}, Existing i)
        else Some (None, Existing j)
    end
| None => None
end = Some (None, dmiddle)

‚àÉ sj : vstate X,
  equivocator_state_project destination j = Some sj

    equivocator_vlsm_transition_item_project item
      (Existing i)
  with
  | Some (Some item', odescriptor) =>
      Some (item' :: tr, odescriptor)
  | Some (None, odescriptor) => Some (tr, odescriptor)
  | None => None
  end = Some (tr0, Existing i)

Definition equivocator_label_zero_project (l : equivocator_label X) : option (vlabel X) :=
  match l with
  | ContinueWith 0 li => Some li
  | _ => None
  end.
